"```sql\nSELECT b.event_status\nFROM expense e\nJOIN budget b ON e.link_to_budget = b.budget_id\nWHERE e.expense_description = 'Post Cards, Posters'\n  AND e.expense_date = '2019-08-20';\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the `event_status` from the `budget` table by joining it with the `expense` table using the `link_to_budget` foreign key. It filters the results to find the expense with the description 'Post Cards, Posters' and the date '2019-08-20'."